# CrossUserDataset archive checksums
#
# This file will be populated with the MD5 hashes of the D1 / D2 / D3 archives
# at the time of public release on Harvard Dataverse. Format matches GNU md5sum
# so that users can verify downloads with:
#
#   md5sum -c metadata/checksums.md5
#
# Each line will read:  <md5-hash>  <filename>
#
# Placeholders below will be replaced with real hashes on acceptance.

TBD-on-acceptance  D1.zip
TBD-on-acceptance  D2.zip
TBD-on-acceptance  D3.zip
